data.description: The perfect starter home! This 3 bedroom 2 bath single family home with a pool in the rapid developing area of Lehigh Acres. Interior features an open floor plan with vaulted ceiling, master bedroom & private ensuite with walking closet, the additional two bedrooms are currently being used as a private separate living area but can easily be reverted back to its original two bedrooms, the exterior features a large driveway with a 2 car garage, space to store an RV or Boat, covered patio area with pool and spa, the ideal backyard for family gathering and entertaining.
